msgctxt "60ｆ以下です	　	分	59	255	34"
msgid "Not long ago, I did a magazine interview. When it\\r\n"
"was announced you'd be in the Princess League finals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	119	375	256"
msgid "My ex-husband naturally caught wind...\\r\n"
"and sent me this letter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	712	647"
msgid "He asked me to meet him in Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	123	957	834"
msgid "Truth be told, I thought I'd never see him again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	95	1079	984"
msgid "He chose to walk a path I\\r\n"
"could never follow him down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	116	1200	1084"
msgid "Until now, I hadn't heard a single word from him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	1274	1214"
msgid "Ma'am..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	141	1455	1314"
msgid "But, this is so important to you.\\r\n"
"I can't possibly accept it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	1522	1462"
msgid "Of course you can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	122	1690	1568"
msgid "Though actually, there's something I need in return."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	149	1891	1742"
msgid "Haruka. I have... a favor to ask of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60ｆ以下です	　	　	41	1953	1912"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	148	2102	1954"
msgid "It's been so long since I've seen my ex...\\r\n"
"I've aged more than I care to admit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	107	2252	2145"
msgid "I... don't want him to be\\r\n"
"disappointed in what he sees."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	105	2409	2304"
msgid "Do you think you could meet him in my place?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	146	2567	2421"
msgid "Afterward, you can bring him over to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	156	2762	2606"
msgid "I'd prefer he didn't see this old,\\r\n"
"haggard face in any bright light."
