msgctxt " 	　	　	71	2839	2768"
msgid "I'll do anything you ask me to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	137	3002	2865"
msgid "But you have nothing to worry about.\\r\n"
"I think you're beautiful, Park-san."
